  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, bioinspired approaches, such as machine learning-integrated hydrogels, are being explored for their potential in distinguishing complex taste types and interactions (Miao et al. 2024).",
    "Table 2 summarizes recent studies focused on gustatory research, highlighting diverse applications of AI in flavor analysis, such as the use of AI for predicting taste properties, addressing data imbalance in taste categorization, and enhancing consumer preference modeling.",
    "These studies demonstrate the growing integration of AI in advancing both the precision of taste detection and the customization of flavor experiences.",
    "The integration of AI in gustatory research not only enhances the scientific understanding of taste but also has practical applications across various sectors.",
    "AI's capabilities in data analysis and predictive modeling are transforming culinary arts and health sectors, leading to innovative solutions that improve both food experiences and nutritional outcomes."
